reviewText: I love this DVD collection, however I wish it was stated that this DVD is just Halloween based episodes taken from the original series. Otherwise I love it.

I had forgotten how funny this show was! The quick wit followed by perfect sound effects & awesomely creepy animation make each episode just fly by! This is a great collection w/ many episodes directly related to Halloween. This purchase makes me want to get the full series!

LOVED the Beetlejuice cartoon as a kid. Bought it to share with my nephew. He's not as into it, but I'll try again when he's a little older. In the meantime, my boyfriend digs it, so he's always pestering me to watch it!
Don't buy this if you plan on buying the seasons on DVD. It's just a repeat of episodes that are already on the season sets. Still a great show though :)

Bettlejuice was my favorite cartoon as a kid and I still love it. This dvd is the Halloween episodes from the series so if you have the series already don't get it. If your interested in watching Bettlejuice and you can't afford the entire series this is a great place to start. If you love Tim Burton then you'll love this cartoon. I would recommend this for anyone 8 and older.
